            <p>It started with the pairing of Asthine’s charm with Andres’ energy. The rest is ASHDRES-tory!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card border-danger shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-danger">👑 Mutya ng Section E</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Crowned with confidence, ASHDRES ruled the classroom.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card border-warning shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-warning">🎤 Crowd Favorites</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Their performance? Electric. Their presence? Unmatched.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card border-success shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title text-success">💫 Legendary Status</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Even after the event, ASHDRES became the pride of Section E.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info mt-5 text-center">
        🌟 ASHDRES isn't just a pair — it's Ashtine Olviga and Andres Mulach!
    </div>
